        <detaileddescription>
<para>loads and merges a point cloud from a folder with the results of a multi-scan capture: the folder is expected to contain pairs of files named &lt;posePrefix&gt;NNN&lt;poseExt&gt; and &lt;scanPrefix&gt;NNN.ply with matching indices NNN (the number of pairs is arbitrary); each transformation file stores a 4x4 row-major rigid transformation, which is applied to the points (and normals) loaded from the .ply file with the same index; <simplesect kind="return"><para>the union of all transformed points from all found pairs, expressed in the common coordinate frame </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
